author: Matt Pearce
title: Alt-right activist Richard Spencer booted from Conservative Political Action Conference
text:
Feb. 23, 2017, 9:06 a.m. 
A look at President Trump's administration and the rest of Washington:   rescinds Obama-era guidance New Homeland Security memos call for strengthening immigration enforcement Trump, after failing to denounce anti-Semitism, calls threats to Jews 'horrible' Trump's new national security advisor , H.R. McMaster, is an Army strategist Defense secretary says the U.S. has no desire to seize Iraq's oil, as Trump has suggested The White House has found ways to end DACA protections while shielding Trump from blowback Feb. 23, 2017, 9:06 a.m. Alt-right activist Richard Spencer booted from Conservative Political Action Conference
